{
  "video_id": "a_avBsX60-s",
  "title": "Fun, fierce and fantastical African art | Wanuri Kahiu",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12804.0,
      "end_time": 15768.0,
      "text": "So, my mother&#39;s a pediatrician,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15792.0,
      "end_time": 19606.0,
      "text": "and when I was young, she&#39;d tell the craziest stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19630.0,
      "end_time": 22852.0,
      "text": "that combined science with her overactive imagination."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23444.0,
      "end_time": 27595.0,
      "text": "One of the stories she told was that if you eat a lot of salt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27619.0,
      "end_time": 31288.0,
      "text": "all of the blood rushes up your legs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31312.0,
      "end_time": 32564.0,
      "text": "through your body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32588.0,
      "end_time": 34667.0,
      "text": "and shoots out the top of your head,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34691.0,
      "end_time": 36393.0,
      "text": "killing you instantly."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36417.0,
      "end_time": 37477.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37501.0,
      "end_time": 39312.0,
      "text": "She called it \"high blood pressure.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39337.0,
      "end_time": 40981.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41500.0,
      "end_time": 43915.0,
      "text": "This was my first experience with science fiction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43939.0,
      "end_time": 45224.0,
      "text": "and I loved it."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45771.0,
      "end_time": 48898.0,
      "text": "So when I started to write my own science fiction and fantasy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48922.0,
      "end_time": 51416.0,
      "text": "I was surprised that it was considered un-African."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 52114.0,
      "end_time": 54729.0,
      "text": "So naturally, I asked, what is African?"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54753.0,
      "end_time": 56613.0,
      "text": "And this is what I know so far:"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 57555.0,
      "end_time": 59770.0,
      "text": "Africa is important."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 59843.0,
      "end_time": 61274.0,
      "text": "Africa is the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 61298.0,
      "end_time": 62564.0,
      "text": "It is, though."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 63740.0,
      "end_time": 67396.0,
      "text": "And Africa is a serious place where only serious things happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 67421.0,
      "end_time": 71896.0,
      "text": "So when I present my work somewhere, someone will always ask,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 71920.0,
      "end_time": 74491.0,
      "text": "\"What&#39;s so important about it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 74515.0,
      "end_time": 77340.0,
      "text": "How does it deal with real African issues"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 77580.0,
      "end_time": 82426.0,
      "text": "like war, poverty, devastation or AIDS?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 82450.0,
      "end_time": 83659.0,
      "text": "And it doesn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 84107.0,
      "end_time": 89444.0,
      "text": "My work is about Nairobi pop bands that want to go to space"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 89468.0,
      "end_time": 92596.0,
      "text": "or about seven-foot-tall robots"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 92620.0,
      "end_time": 94920.0,
      "text": "that fall in love."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 94493.0,
      "end_time": 97705.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s nothing incredibly important."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 97730.0,
      "end_time": 101113.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just fun, fierce and frivolous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 101137.0,
      "end_time": 103748.0,
      "text": "as frivolous as bubble gum --"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 103772.0,
      "end_time": 105107.0,
      "text": "\"AfroBubbleGum.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 106241.0,
      "end_time": 109506.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m not saying that agenda art isn&#39;t important;"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 109530.0,
      "end_time": 111805.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m the chairperson of a charity"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 111829.0,
      "end_time": 118785.0,
      "text": "that deals with films and theaters that write about HIV and radicalization"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 118810.0,
      "end_time": 121730.0,
      "text": "and female genital mutilation."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 121970.0,
      "end_time": 123378.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s vital and important art,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 123402.0,
      "end_time": 126954.0,
      "text": "but it cannot be the only art that comes out of the continent."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 128192.0,
      "end_time": 130528.0,
      "text": "We have to tell more stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 130550.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131966.0,
      "text": "that are vibrant."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 133970.0,
      "end_time": 137480.0,
      "text": "The danger of the single story is still being realized."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 137879.0,
      "end_time": 139697.0,
      "text": "And maybe it&#39;s because of the funding."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 139722.0,
      "end_time": 143625.0,
      "text": "A lot of art is still dependent on developmental aid."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 143649.0,
      "end_time": 146515.0,
      "text": "So art becomes a tool for agenda."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 147730.0,
      "end_time": 152148.0,
      "text": "Or maybe it&#39;s because we&#39;ve only seen one image of ourselves for so long"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 152172.0,
      "end_time": 154619.0,
      "text": "that that&#39;s all we know how to create."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 154643.0,
      "end_time": 157816.0,
      "text": "Whatever the reason, we need a new way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 157840.0,
      "end_time": 159685.0,
      "text": "and AfroBubbleGum is one approach."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 160391.0,
      "end_time": 163686.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the advocacy of art for art&#39;s sake."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 164489.0,
      "end_time": 167485.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the advocacy of art that is not policy-driven"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 167509.0,
      "end_time": 169410.0,
      "text": "or agenda-driven"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 169650.0,
      "end_time": 171400.0,
      "text": "or based on education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 171280.0,
      "end_time": 174394.0,
      "text": "just for the sake of imagination:"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 174418.0,
      "end_time": 175971.0,
      "text": "AfroBubbleGum art."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 176649.0,
      "end_time": 179350.0,
      "text": "And we can&#39;t all be AfroBubbleGumists."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 179590.0,
      "end_time": 183105.0,
      "text": "We have to judge our work for its potential poverty porn pitfalls."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 183129.0,
      "end_time": 186382.0,
      "text": "We have to have tests that are similar to the Bechdel test,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 189184.0,
      "end_time": 190897.0,
      "text": "and ask questions like:"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 191475.0,
      "end_time": 195430.0,
      "text": "Are two or more Africans in this piece of fiction healthy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 196916.0,
      "end_time": 202111.0,
      "text": "Are those same Africans financially stable and not in need of saving?"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 203193.0,
      "end_time": 206810.0,
      "text": "Are they having fun and enjoying life?"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 206105.0,
      "end_time": 209203.0,
      "text": "And if we can answer yes to two or more of these questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 209227.0,
      "end_time": 211198.0,
      "text": "then surely we&#39;re AfroBubbleGumists."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 211855.0,
      "end_time": 213404.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 213428.0,
      "end_time": 218204.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 218229.0,
      "end_time": 219718.0,
      "text": "And fun is political,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 220267.0,
      "end_time": 224519.0,
      "text": "because imagine if we have images of Africans who were vibrant"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 224543.0,
      "end_time": 226586.0,
      "text": "and loving and thriving"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 226610.0,
      "end_time": 228898.0,
      "text": "and living a beautiful, vibrant life."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 228922.0,
      "end_time": 231303.0,
      "text": "What would we think of ourselves then?"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 231327.0,
      "end_time": 234174.0,
      "text": "Would we think that maybe we&#39;re worthy of more happiness?"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 234799.0,
      "end_time": 238638.0,
      "text": "Would we think of our shared humanity through our shared joy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 239387.0,
      "end_time": 241317.0,
      "text": "I think of these things when I create."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 241767.0,
      "end_time": 244968.0,
      "text": "I think of the people and the places that give me immeasurable joy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 244992.0,
      "end_time": 246975.0,
      "text": "and I work to represent them."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 246999.0,
      "end_time": 248636.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s why I write stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 248660.0,
      "end_time": 253130.0,
      "text": "about futuristic girls that risk everything to save plants"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 253154.0,
      "end_time": 255383.0,
      "text": "or to race camels"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 255407.0,
      "end_time": 257847.0,
      "text": "or even just to dance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 257870.0,
      "end_time": 259591.0,
      "text": "to honor fun,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 259616.0,
      "end_time": 261738.0,
      "text": "because my world is mostly happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 261762.0,
      "end_time": 265532.0,
      "text": "And I know happiness is a privilege in this current splintered world"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 265557.0,
      "end_time": 269311.0,
      "text": "where remaining hopeful requires diligence."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 271105.0,
      "end_time": 276448.0,
      "text": "But maybe, if you join me in creating, curating and commissioning"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 276472.0,
      "end_time": 278501.0,
      "text": "more AfroBubbleGum art,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 278525.0,
      "end_time": 281303.0,
      "text": "there might be hope for a different view of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 281327.0,
      "end_time": 283483.0,
      "text": "a happy Africa view"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 283507.0,
      "end_time": 285535.0,
      "text": "where children are strangely traumatized"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 285559.0,
      "end_time": 287502.0,
      "text": "by their mother&#39;s dark sense of humor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 287526.0,
      "end_time": 288563.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 288587.0,
      "end_time": 293149.0,
      "text": "but also they&#39;re claiming fun, fierce and frivolous art"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 293173.0,
      "end_time": 297378.0,
      "text": "in the name of all things unseriously African."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 297910.0,
      "end_time": 300532.0,
      "text": "Because we&#39;re AfroBubbleGumists"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 300556.0,
      "end_time": 303409.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s so many more of us than you can imagine."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 303910.0,
      "end_time": 305114.0,
      "text": "Thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 305138.0,
      "end_time": 308969.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}